free_txt: The targets were made by vacuum evaporation of the
separated isotopes onto thin carbon films about
10 mug/cm**2 thick. The target thicknesses were
Cr-50  more or equal 96.9% , Cr-52 2.69%, Cr-53 less
or equal 0.2%, Cr-54 less or equal 0.02%.
